From: bot-web patch <patch@bot-web>
Subject: Add initTakeoutSession, finishTakeoutSession, getLeftChats

Adds three new methods to the TDLib public API:
- initTakeoutSession: opens account.initTakeoutSession on the server
- finishTakeoutSession: calls account.finishTakeoutSession
- getLeftChats: calls channels.getLeftChannels wrapped in invokeWithTakeout

These expose enumeration of channels and supergroups the current user has
left — functionality not otherwise available in the TDLib public API.

